{"name":"Rhedda Blud","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"Orc","alignment":"LN","hitDice":"10","armorName":"breastplate","shieldBonus":2,"natArmorBonus":5,"otherArmorDesc":"12","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"75 (10d8 + 30)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"16","dexPoints":"14","conPoints":"16","intPoints":"10","wisPoints":"10","chaPoints":"10","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"5","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"[MON] can take 1 villain action, choosing from the options below. Only one Villain action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. [MON] regains spent villain actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the spy can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the spy can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The spy can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the spy's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the spy's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the spy dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"[MON] makes two weapon attacks. [MON] may also use Unleash Incarnation once if it has uses remaining."},{"name":"Battleaxe","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1D8] slashing damage (or [STR 1d10] if wielding with both hands)"},{"name":"Javelin","desc":"_Melee or Ranged Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft. or range 30/120 ft., one target. Hit: [STR 1D6] piercing damage."},{"name":"Unleash Incarnation (3/Day)","desc":"[MON] makes one melee weapon attack from its echo's position."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Manifest Echo","desc":"[MON] magically manifests an echo of itself in an unoccupied space it can see within 15 feet. The echo is a magical, translucent, gray image of the knight that lasts until it is destroyed or [MON] dismisses it as a bonus action, manifests another echo, is incapacitated, or is more than 30 feet away from the echo at the end of its turn.\nThe echo has an AC of 16, 1 hit point, and is immune to all conditions. If it has to make a saving throw, it uses [MON]'s saving throw modifiers. It is the same size as [MON], and occupies its space. On [MON]'s turn, it can mentally command the echo to move up to 30 feet without using an action.\nWhile the echo is manifested, [MON] has the following benefits:\n\nAs a bonus action, [MON] magically swaps places with its echo at a cost of 15 feet of movement.\nWhen [MON] attacks, it can attack from its own space or from the echo's space.\nOther creatures provoke opportunity attacks when they move away from the echo, as if [MON] was standing in the echo's space."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Shadow Martyr (Recharge 6)","desc":"When a creature [MON] can see is attacked, before the attack roll is made, the echo teleports to a space within 5 feet of the targeted creature. That attack is made against the echo instead of the original target."},{"name":"Sentinel","desc":"When [MON] hits a creature with an opportunity attack, the creature's speed becomes 0 for the rest of the turn.\nCreatures provoke opportunity attacks from [MON] even if they take the Disengage action before leaving your reach.\nWhen a creature within 5 feet of [MON]/echo makes an attack against a target other than [MON]/echo (and that target doesn't have this feat), [MON] can use her reaction to make a melee weapon attack against the attacking creature."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"con","order":2}],"skills":[{"name":"athletics","stat":"str"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Orc","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Rhedda","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":4,"damage":[]}